{"tid":1978733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普︰中國若對疫情負責任就要面臨後果","createTime":"2020-04-19T02:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T03:32:31.000Z","uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"610168979ac68fb7de3970b695268c7bc6c13504","tid":1978733,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:40:13.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，如果中國對新型冠狀病毒疫情負有責任，將面臨後果。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮記者會上說，錯誤就是錯誤，但如果有責任要負，就肯定會有後果。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普近日批評中國在武漢出現疫情後欠缺透明度，又質疑中國公布的死亡人數。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521435-20200419.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521435-20200419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=d43804fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521435-20200419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=be2de537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521435-20200419.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a97433c0838f98f3fe4a8accca1e5db8e8873e9c","tid":1978733,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HvAOvj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HvAOvj.gif&h=180a04c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8963d310a879e2118e88a1d0454c03901c44d32","tid":1978733,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"Twitter 留言預測：<br />\n<br />\nStop playing the blame game！<br />\nThe world is one family, we should be united to fight with it.<br />\nThe pandemic is borderless. <br />\nThis helps nothing to find out who is to blame at this moment.<br />\nPeace and love are the greatest power in the world.<br />\nThanks WHO, thanks China."},{"pid":"5f54feac25423da883e4a1466daa453b1d73d98e","tid":1978733,"uid":288707,"like"